<note n="0264001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0264001">協會本為摩訶西瓦。</note>
<note n="0265002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0265002">協會本為摩庫羅伽。</note>
<note n="0265003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0265003">協會本為吉利內羅瓦哈那伽。</note>
<note n="0267004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0267004">此章，協會本為五王章，錫蘭本為六王章。此前者為摩訶西瓦，蘇羅提薩、塞那、古達伽、阿塞羅，耶羅羅之中塞那、古達伽之二王名為一王之名處理。</note>
</p>
